  "detailed_description": "<h1>More games</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/eb57bb7e7d4e4155f7d94282cf1d6c14.poster.avif?t=1706729389\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/eb57bb7e7d4e4155f7d94282cf1d6c14.webm?t=1706729389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/eb57bb7e7d4e4155f7d94282cf1d6c14.mp4?t=1706729389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you ready to fight and beat enemies with your fighting skills or with<br>using diffrent weapons. Let's go!!!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/637fc6c15db4f481ec87a0c79600b98e.poster.avif?t=1706729389\" width=560 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/637fc6c15db4f481ec87a0c79600b98e.webm?t=1706729389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/637fc6c15db4f481ec87a0c79600b98e.mp4?t=1706729389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>GAMEPLAY:<br><br>You choose your character out of 8 available, at the begining only two are unlocked.<br>The main task is to fight enemies on your way and surviving through the next stages.<br>To defeat the enemies you may use fighting skills, all characters have different fighting styles, but you can also use different weapons and many power ups.<br>You may collect currency and upgrade your character or you can buy new ones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/14eda81f6d06658e946504e710ffeca7.poster.avif?t=1706729389\" width=560 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/14eda81f6d06658e946504e710ffeca7.webm?t=1706729389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/14eda81f6d06658e946504e710ffeca7.mp4?t=1706729389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>FEATURES:<br><br>- 12 beautiful different stages,<br>- Buy and upgrade characters,<br>- 8 characters with different fighting styles, <br>- Many Power ups,<br>- Lots of different weapons to use such as : axes, swords, hammers and guns,<br>- Many various opponents to fight<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/728ced53c0f46dfd3e72643855216016.poster.avif?t=1706729389\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/728ced53c0f46dfd3e72643855216016.webm?t=1706729389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450410/extras/728ced53c0f46dfd3e72643855216016.mp4?t=1706729389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
